recaptcha\" data-sitekey=\"6LdtFHIhAAAAAENXS8JO7-KljjwNvLYnJjJRb5gX\" data-type=\"v3\" data-action=\"Form\" data-badge=\"inline\" data-size=\"invisible\"><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-field-group elementor-column elementor-field-type-submit elementor-col-100 e-form__buttons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<button class=\"elementor-button elementor-size-sm\" type=\"submit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Send<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/button>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/form>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-78de713 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"78de713\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bbb4039\" data-id=\"bbb4039\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92cdeca elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"92cdeca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Habitat &amp; Behavior of fire ants<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2707c61 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2707c61\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Fire ants, also known as red imported fire ants, are social insects that can be found living in a wide variety of habitats. They build their nests, called mounds, by pushing up the soil as they tunnel into the earth and can nest in almost any type of soil. However, they prefer open, sunny areas such as meadows, pastures, parks, playgrounds, lawns, and golf courses. Fire ants are highly aggressive and territorial, and a complex social structure characterizes their Behavior. Each fire ant colony has a queen, female workers, and male drones. The queen is responsible for laying eggs, while the workers are responsible for tending to the young, foraging for food, and defending the colony against intruders. The drones, however, are responsible for mating with the queen. When a fire ant colony is disturbed, the ants will aggressively defend their nest by swarming and stinging any perceived threat. Their stings can be painful and cause itching, burning, and swelling in humans and other animals. Fire ants also have a unique ability to link their bodies together to form a floating mass, which they use to survive flooding or other natural disasters.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-850f1e6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"850f1e6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Symptoms of a fire ant bite<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25e32f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"25e32f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Fire ants are small but dangerous insects that can cause severe pain and discomfort when they bite humans. The symptoms of a fire ant bite vary depending on the individual&#8217;s sensitivity to the venom and the number of bites received. Generally, a fire ant bite is characterized by an immediate burning sensation that feels like a sharp sting, followed by intense itching and swelling at the site of the bite.<\/p><p>In most cases, redness and raised bumps will also appear around the bite area, which may become painful or tender over time. Other common symptoms associated with fire ant bites include nausea, headaches, dizziness or difficulty breathing in people who are allergic to insect stings.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c89288d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c89288d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Prevention tips for preventing fire ants from invading<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd78daa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bd78daa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Fire ants are a common nuisance in many parts of the world, and their stings can be extremely painful. To prevent these pesky insects from invading your property, there are several things you can do.<\/p><ul><li>First, keep your yard clear of debris and clutter. Fire ants love to build nests in piles of wood or leaves, so removing these materials from your yard is a great way to discourage them.<\/li><li>Another effective prevention tip is to keep your lawn well-maintained. Frequent mowing will keep your grass looking neat and make it less attractive for fire ant colonies to establish themselves.<\/li><li>Consider using insecticides or bait stations specifically designed for fire ant control. These products can be applied around the perimeter of your property, creating a barrier that prevents new colonies from moving in.<\/li><li>The best way to control fire ants is first to identify their locations and then treat the areas where they are active. A variety of treatments available at ACME Pest Solutions can be effective in controlling fire ants.<\/li><\/ul><p>Taking preventative measures against fire ants is key to maintaining a safe and comfortable living space free from any unwanted pests. By proactively reducing potential nesting sites and applying targeted insecticide treatments as needed, homeowners can enjoy peace of mind knowing that their properties are protected against this common pest problem.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b7ebf39 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b7ebf39\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ba1cf99\" data-id=\"ba1cf99\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b755c37\" data-id=\"b755c37\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c3d98e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7c3d98e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Residential Pest Control Service<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-595ca92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"595ca92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Customized pest control treatments can be used to safeguard your living space against bothersome pests and ensure that they don&#8217;t become a nuisance in your home.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1265dc elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-global elementor-global-4670 elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"c1265dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/appointment\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book An Appointment<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d243229\" data-id=\"d243229\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fire Ants Identification Color Size Description Color Regarding coloration, fire ants vary depending on the